title: 海底神殿的全部方块在材质包的哪个位置？
author: Noble_yT
txt_content: RT 是海底神殿的全部方块在材质包的哪个位置？

replies.author: 爱心魔王FHC
replies.txt_content:
\assets\minecraft\textures\blocks
海晶石砖 prismarine_bricks.png
海晶石 prismarine_rough.png
暗海晶石 prismarine_dark.png
海晶灯 sea_lantern.png
湿海绵 sea_lantern.png

replies.author: xieyanze
replies.txt_content:
解压游戏目录下.minecraft\versions\（对应游戏版本，至少1.9＋）.zip
解压后在assets\minecraft\textures\blocks
找
prismarine_bricks.png
prismarine_dark.png
prismarine_rough.png
